        "meta_description": "TV executive Dick Ebersol had just dropped off his wife, Kate & Allie star Susan Saint James, in Colorado when his private jet took off into snowy conditions with Ebersol and the couple's two sons — 14-year-old Teddy and 21-year-old Charlie — aboard",
